                    <ab>
                        <lb n="1"/><persName corresp="#asteria">Ennia Asteria</persName>, <persName corresp="#asterius">Enni Asteri</persName> filia,
                        <lb n="2"/>ex origine <persName corresp="#cerealis">Enni Cerealis</persName> avi sui arcam
                        <lb n="3"/>suo nomine renovavit, quam post ex
                        <lb n="4" break="no"/>cessum suum si quis <choice><reg>irrumperit</reg><orig>inruperit</orig></choice> inferet fisci
                        <lb n="5"/>rationibus <measure type="fine" unit="sestertius" quantity="200"><choice><reg>sestertium</reg><orig>HS</orig></choice> <num value="200">CC</num> <choice><abbr>N</abbr><expan>N<ex>ummum</ex></expan></choice></measure>. Fili sane veniam habebunt.
                    </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
