            <div type="translation">
                <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                    <p>
                        <persName corresp="#asteria" xml:lang="la">Ennia Asteria</persName>, daughter of <persName corresp="#asterius" xml:lang="la">Ennius Asterius</persName>, restored in her own name the arca that had belonged to her grandfather <persName corresp="#cerealis" xml:lang="la">Ennius Cerealis</persName>.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        If anyone should violate it after her death, he shall pay two hundred sesterces to the accounts of the <term xml:lang="la">fiscus</term>. Her children, however, shall be exempt.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div type="translation" xml:lang="it">
                    <p>
                        <persName corresp="#asteria" xml:lang="la">Ennia Asteria</persName>, figlia di <persName corresp="#asterius" xml:lang="la">Ennius Asterius</persName>, restaurò a suo nome l’arca che era stata del nonno <persName corresp="#cerealis" xml:lang="la">Ennius Cerealis</persName>.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Se qualcuno, dopo la sua morte, dovesse violarla, pagherà alle casse del <term xml:lang="la">fiscus</term> duecento sesterzi. I figli, tuttavia, ne saranno esentati.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
